ComicInfo.Title: --But Dr. Blake Can Die!
ComicInfo.Summary: --But Dr. Blake Can Die!: Loki has stolen Thor's hammer and fled to Midgard. Thor and Sif pursue him, but without the hammer Thor changes into Don Blake as Loki attacks them. Loki escapes, but Sif is injured in the fight, and Dr. Blake must operate to save her life.
